{"tid":1978920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣成功試射威力加強版薩德 支那官媒爆氣：匪軍將別無選擇","createTime":"2020-04-19T05:15:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T14:58:46.000Z","uid":32511,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"e37272c7a7232657e070b6d9a252628699640a7b","tid":1978920,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T05:15:22.000Z","msg":"日前台東地區傳出巨大聲響，在地方社團引發討論，經過進一步追蹤，這是國家中山科學研究院所進行的「天弓三型防空飛彈」試射計畫，未來系統有望進行量產，強化國軍攔截飛彈的防禦能力。對此，大陸國台辦旗下媒體《中國台灣網》再度向台灣提出威嚇，強調「解放軍別無選擇，必將不惜一戰，不惜一切代價，堅決維護祖國統一。」<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/01/09/1726432-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F01%2F09%2F1726432-XXL.jpg&h=5ac7e8b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/09/11/1537765-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F09%2F11%2F1537765-XXL.jpg&h=691bfdd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國軍試射計畫，時間是落在4月9日至4月14日，地點則選在台東縣三仙台。主角「天弓三型」，攔截敵方飛彈的高度可達到45公里，中科院也在進行性能強化，並命名為「強弓專案」，希望發揮「台版薩德」的領空防禦能力。<br />\n <br />\n聽聞台灣此次試射計畫，官媒《中國台灣網》相當不滿，認為這樣的作為是「以武拒統」，中方必須提高警覺，同時搬出慣用的「祖國統一」話術，直言解放軍將別無選擇，將會不惜一切代價，堅決維護祖國領土的完整與統一。"},{"pid":"77396c725a91699d2946104054f06567348bd582","tid":1978920,"uid":2383,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T05:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A8MwnHt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA8MwnHt.jpg&h=2fd967c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n衰軟必豬"},{"pid":"3e4795ebc9c6966595d8a44dcf0d2e8b0e00980b","tid":1978920,"uid":69746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T05:20:06.000Z","msg":"出兵未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得撚個講字<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dde3a613246d826801481600dce7a8d2dc6316c1","tid":1978920,"uid":262093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T05:27:39.000Z","msg":"日日都爆氣唔攰架咩"},{"pid":"367bd4c754a5aa795a305a936489a5af6a2ac505","tid":1978920,"uid":53577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T14:29:31.000Z","msg":"導彈防禦系統一定要配合本身嘅核攻擊能力,<br />\n主要係提高己方嘅抗核打擊生存能力, 如果唔係邊防得晒."},{"pid":"5024383c01ac110fc22e8c5bf3652b654c2ce8c6","tid":1978920,"uid":291947,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T14:33:33.000Z","msg":"孫仔：阿爺，共產黨話要打過黎啊～<br />\n爺爺：幹！我已經聽了70年！"},{"pid":"f1c0ab24712cbb73f8e483c089079e37f1e5fac9","tid":1978920,"uid":205469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T14:41:15.000Z","msg":"射防空導彈有咩問題？<br />\n打唔打到地面/海面目標？<br />\n只要你唔入去人哋領空就冇事"},{"pid":"f0179146f5ed2f4a25b0c751137d97502588573f","tid":1978920,"uid":2752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T14:43:04.000Z","msg":"你唔去現場就唔會有危險.jpg"},{"pid":"a86a9da2101d7cb65eaca98b286885d20e342125","tid":1978920,"uid":32675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T14:45:39.000Z","msg":"核彈加中程飛彈可保台灣"},{"pid":"a207fedd58df9c2f8f0073f0fa53794653615e03","tid":1978920,"uid":127401,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T14:47:21.000Z","msg":"成身刀既人<br />\n話人地個盾危鳩險你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d88dcc7560f11d41a9919f70d7a9996935270f2","tid":1978920,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T14:48:48.000Z","msg":"屌你講咗三十年都唔止，仲未出兵？"},{"pid":"e56d45e9f36b71a89b339679e3ec467be4624a86","tid":1978920,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T14:48:55.000Z","msg":"派錢或有著數俾班支狗將軍，想佢地認乜都得，互相出賣都無問題，中國就係盛產漢奸既地方😏"},{"pid":"4ea108288efe3bc91bd8319ccd8eac0d50d34638","tid":1978920,"uid":297045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d88dcc7560f11d41a9919f70d7a9996935270f2","tid":1978920,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T14:48:48.